Should I

00:06:06.290 --> 00:06:07.930
intercept both of them

00:06:08.210 --> 00:06:09.610
and inspect their cargo?

00:06:09.780 --> 00:06:10.710
That won't work.

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:14.800
Zhou Kui arranged for two caravans to
depart simultaneously

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:16.560
to prevent any incidents.

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:19.280
If we intercept both caravans,

00:06:19.460 --> 00:06:20.290
I'm afraid

00:06:21.560 --> 00:06:22.840
it will alert Zhou Kui.

