Besides,

00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:29.600
Shu is still in his hands.

00:06:39.050 --> 00:06:40.590
The guards near the Imperial City

00:06:40.590 --> 00:06:42.790
will take at least three days to arrive.

00:06:43.420 --> 00:06:45.020
If we alert our enemies,

00:06:45.050 --> 00:06:46.380
I'm afraid that Zhou Kui

00:06:46.590 --> 00:06:48.720
might become desperate and reckless.

00:06:49.880 --> 00:06:50.810
Our current plan

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:53.440
